name: Gym Bros: LooksMaxx
summary: Skip leg day, grab your bros, and get SWOL. Pump until your arms pop, climb like a protein-fuelled gorilla, pose and compete for Looks (clout) in front of streaming mirrors. The world is watching as you and your friends flex and race to show-off your chiselled virtual physique. Customize your bro, hit the dance floor, or just hang out. Will you strike a cringe pose or giga-Chad your way to the podium? Play for free and maybe buy us a protein shake on Ko-fi. Skip Leg Day. Stay Swol.
